## What Is This?
{{PROJECT_DESCRIPTION}}

This is a management repo — no applications are built here.
Configuration, skills, hooks and agents are managed and deployed to target paths.

## Repository Structure
{{REPO_STRUCTURE}}

## Deployment
- Master copies live in this repo
- `bash setup.sh` deploys to target paths
- Changes: Edit here first, then run setup to sync

## Quality Standards
- ShellCheck all .sh files
- Valid JSON for all .json files
- No secrets in committed files
- No hardcoded versions

## Git & CI/CD
- Conventional Commits (feat:, fix:, docs:, chore:)
- CI must pass before merge (ShellCheck, JSON, secret scan)
